# =============================================================================
# ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES - DOCUMENTATION ONLY
# =============================================================================
#
# This file documents the environment variables used by this project.
# ACTUAL VALUES are stored in Supabase secrets (for edge functions) and are
# never committed to the repository.
#
# For Vercel deployments, public values (Supabase URL, anon key) are hardcoded
# in the client code since they are publishable and safe for public repos.
#
# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE (Stored in Supabase secrets for edge functions)
# =============================================================================
# SUPABASE_URL - Project URL (also hardcoded in client for public access)
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY - Publishable anon key (also hardcoded in client)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY - Server-side only, never exposed to client
#
# =============================================================================
# GHL CHAT WIDGET (Stored in Supabase secrets, fetched via edge function)
# =============================================================================
# GHL_LOCATION_ID - GoHighLevel location identifier
# GHL_WIDGET_ID - Default widget ID (legacy, use specific IDs below)
# GHL_WIDGET_ID_SALES - Sales chat widget
# GHL_WIDGET_ID_SUPPORT - Support/help chat widget  
# GHL_WIDGET_ID_DEMO - Demo request chat widget
# GHL_WIDGET_ID_LOCALPROS - LocalPros vertical chat widget
#
# =============================================================================
# GITHUB (Stored in Supabase secrets for theme sync edge function)
# =============================================================================
# GITHUB_PAT - Personal access token for repo operations
# GITHUB_REPO_OWNER - Repository owner
# GITHUB_REPO_NAME - Repository name
#
# =============================================================================
